    "chemicalDescription": [
      "s-HIV-1 Oligopeptide-2 SP is a single chain protein containing 55 amino acids. It is synthetically produced based on the sequence for Gag-Pol Polyprotein which is found in the pathogenic virus, Human Immunodeficiency Virus-1 (HIV-1). It contains 246 amino acids which may contain disulfide bonds and/or glycosylation, and consists of the proper sequence of the 20 amino acids."
